### 3ï¸âƒ£ Reinforcement Learning (Learning by Trial & Error)
ğŸ“Œ How It Works:  
- The model interacts with an environment and learns through rewards and penalties.  
- Used for sequential decision-making problems.  
ğŸ“Œ Examples: 
âœ… Self-driving cars â€“ Learning to navigate roads by trial & error.  
âœ… Game AI (AlphaGo, Chess AI) â€“ Learning to beat human players.  
ğŸ›  Common Algorithms: 
- Q-Learning  
